item.title: Ageless & Unapologetic - Why Confidence Is the New Botox with Angela Miller Kumar
item.description: At 57, Angela Miller Kumar is redefining what it means to be ageless. Model, influencer, and curator of Ageless Vitality, Angela is on a mission to empower women to embrace their individuality, confidence, and sensuality at every stage of life. Her philosophy? It’s not about chasing youth — it’s about embodying vitality... Feed: https://feed.pod.co/ihealthradio

item.title: 'One to One: John & Yoko' Director Kevin Macdonald
item.description: Kevin Macdonald knows John Lennon and Yoko Ono are one of the most scrutinized relationships pop culture history. So he took a new approach to these icons: exploring how the TV they were watching from their Manhattan apartment shaped, and reflected, their views of America. IndieWire Doc Toolkit is sponsored by HBO Max. Listen to the Screen Talk Podcast. Every Friday IndieWire editors Anne Thompson & Ryan Lattanzio break down insider news from Hollywood and debate the latest films and series... Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/PMC3965722282
